June Term, 1947

December 19, 1947 Division A Murrell, Fleming & Flowers, for appellant. Broad & Cassel, Keen & O'Kelley, J. Velma Keen and Chas. H. Spitz, for appellees. *894PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on authority of King v. Palm Beach Bank & Trust Co., 92 Fla. 414, 109 So. 580.
